                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-149-off803 t18240916-149-cd804"></join>, a handkerchief, value 4 s, the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240916-149-victim1284" type="victimName">
                           Edward William Corry 
                           Astley
                        <interp inst="t18240916-149-victim1284" type="surname" value="Astley"></interp>
